column5: I swore off moose and deer paintings quite a while ago basically cause everybody was doing them....and  Here I go---this makes #2 in a year.  Maybe I gotta change my brand of beer???  Bushart
High and to the right if they're yours TJ.
Don't kid yerself---I thought about it for a sec      Yeah I could do all this but who'd know what style of porn would hit the canvas---then they'd have to give me a talkin to
Awesome work Terry Even if you said ya wouldn't.... you still have mad skills with the paint brush Great job and thanks for sharing Jacques
